-- BATS exchange says experiencing networking issue; halt on BYX
-- 
-- Thu Sep 26, 2013 10:25am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/26/us-markets-usa-stocks-bats-idUSBRE98P0OR20130926

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - BATS exchange said on Thursday it is experiencing an internal networking issue and that trading was halted on its smaller marketplace, BYX, at 9:44 a.m. ET. 
 BATS said trading on its primary marketplace, BZX, is unaffected. (Reporting by  Caroline Valetkevitch ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )